is a big deal

260
00:12:46,640 --> 00:12:49,040
because they'd all been
subjected to mandatory

261
00:12:49,120 --> 00:12:51,880
minimum sentencing laws,
which is our topic tonight.

262
00:12:51,960 --> 00:12:55,320
Mandatory minimums require judges
to punish certain crimes

263
00:12:55,400 --> 00:12:57,520
with a minimum
number of years in prison

264
00:12:57,600 --> 00:13:00,360
regardless of context,
which is a little strange

265
00:13:00,440 --> 00:13:02,400
