266
00:13:02,480 --> 00:13:04,080
For instance,
like shouting the phrase

267
00:13:04,160 --> 00:13:06,800
"I'm coming !" is fine
when catching a bus,

268
00:13:06,880 --> 00:13:09,680
but not okay when
you're already on the bus.

269
00:13:09,840 --> 00:13:13,320
So, circumstances
make a huge difference.

270
00:13:13,400 --> 00:13:15,480
That's what I'm trying to say.

271
00:13:15,600 --> 00:13:17,880
Now, our current
mandatory minimums

272
00:13:17,960 --> 00:13:20,560
were mostly passed during
the tough-on-crime era

273
00:13:20,640 --> 00:13:22,720
of the 1980s and 90's,
and they're partially

274
00:13:22,800 --> 00:13:25,960
responsible for the explosion
of our prison population.

275
00:13:26,280 --> 00:13:30,000
Since 1980, the prison population
has more than quadrupled.

276
00:13:30,080 --> 00:13:31,680
To put that into perspective,

277
00:13:31,760 --> 00:13:34,840
that means one out of
every 100 adults is locked up.

278
00:13:35,320 --> 00:13:38,840
That's true. We have two million
people incarcerated.

279
00:13:39,200 --> 00:13:41,160
If we keep going
in this direction,

280
00:13:41,320 --> 00:13:45,240
