284
00:13:55,080 --> 00:13:57,000
It was worth it,
but it was a long time.

285
00:13:57,080 --> 00:13:59,480
But it was worth it.
It was worth it.

286
00:13:59,560 --> 00:14:02,480
But that's... two centuries.
But it was...

287
00:14:02,560 --> 00:14:04,680
It was worth it, but...

288
00:14:04,760 --> 00:14:08,400
Mandatory minimums
