317
00:15:42,240 --> 00:15:45,080
Is that what you want ?
Is that what you want ?"

318
00:15:45,880 --> 00:15:48,800
So, suffice the perceived
drug menace, Ronald Reagan,

319
00:15:48,920 --> 00:15:51,520
