00:18:34,680 --> 00:18:36,880
He was a congressional staffer
who helped push

373
00:18:36,960 --> 00:18:38,720
mandatory minimums
in the 90's

374
00:18:38,800 --> 00:18:41,480
because he believed that they were
an effective deterrent.

375
00:18:41,560 --> 00:18:43,600
He later went
to prison for fraud,

376
00:18:43,680 --> 00:18:46,920
