381
00:18:58,560 --> 00:19:00,680
You can... you can do
life sentence for jaywalking.

382
00:19:00,760 --> 00:19:02,120
It's not gonna stop it.

383
00:19:02,200 --> 00:19:03,520
Of course it isn't.

384
00:19:03,600 --> 00:19:06,880
Ridiculously long sentences are not
a great deterrent to crime.

385
00:19:06,960 --> 00:19:09,240
Prison sentences
are a lot like penises.

386
00:19:09,320 --> 00:19:11,680
If they're used correctly,
even a short one

