00:19:13,880 --> 00:19:16,680
...is a rumor I have heard.

389
00:19:17,520 --> 00:19:19,640
And the truth is...

390
00:19:20,200 --> 00:19:22,920
The truth is,
mandatory minimums...

391
00:19:23,600 --> 00:19:26,240
mandatory minimums
didn't just not work,

392
00:19:26,320 --> 00:19:28,040
they ruined lives.

393
00:19:28,120 --> 00:19:30,000
Take the case
