395
00:19:32,280 --> 00:19:35,760
When he was 24, he sold small amounts
of marijuana to an informant

396
00:19:35,840 --> 00:19:38,320
while he happened to have
a gun in his possession.

397
00:19:38,400 --> 00:19:42,040
And as a result, he received
a 55-year mandatory minimum

398
00:19:42,160 --> 00:19:45,280
sentence with no parole.
He won't get out until he's 79

399
00:19:45,920 --> 00:19:48,400
for selling something
that's currently legal

400
00:19:48,480 --> 00:19:50,520
for recreational use
in four states,

401
00:19:50,600 --> 00:19:52,280
and whose main side effect

